{
  "stem": "13251.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And you were asking about do I remember my father what he did as far as clowning around?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Yeah, I remember spending a Purim there and my father getting dressed up, you know, of putting makeup on his face and clowning around.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I remember spending Purim there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Were there other relatives there with you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, just-- just us-- just my family, our family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And let's see, there isn't a whole I remember from that place, because we were confined.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't tell us a thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember one time we went on a field trip-- you know, kids.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In fact, that area I was-- if I recall was called Rote Brucke, which is, in German, Red Bridge.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that was the name of that-- Rote Brucke, yeah, something like that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I guess Slovakia being close to Germany, they used a lot of German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was people from the-- I mean, even though we were in a restricted-- and-- you know, were confined and had limited movement-- I'm sure with passes and stuff, they allowed some freedom.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't like-- it wasn't a concentration camp or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as far as I recall, we were not treated badly at that point.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, it was while we were there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I remember this-- this is when the process started of us going to England, I guess.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember this young, blonde lady, girl, talking to my parents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I haven't the faintest idea what they were talking about.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember her talking to some other families.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
